headline: NCLH Stock Slips 26% in Six Months: Should You Buy, Sell or Hold?

summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Norwegian Cruise Line (NYSE:NCLH) and the best and worst performers in the travel and vacation providers industry.
